EmailTemplate.name: ISDA Amend Next Steps
EmailTemplate.subject: Your IHS Markit Customer Care Case {!Case.CaseNumber} - Counterparty Manager - Next Steps
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Case.Contact},
The below information is to assist with getting you and your team setup to complete Self Disclosure Letter, Variation Margin Protocol, EMIR Classifications, Canadian Representation Letter, Cross Border Representation, Australian Single Sided Reporting Rules, Initial Margin Segregation and/or ISDA Amend Protocol questionnaires. If you have already been contacted by a Counterparty Manager Product Specialist, you can disregard this email.
In order to create your Counterparty Manager account, please send the following information: 1. A tax or legal document showing the true legal name of the Parent Company or Investment Manager. Within the entity structure the Parent Company should be the top level institution presiding over the adhering entities. If you are a paralegal, you will need to provide the documentation of the client you are representing and will need to set up separate accounts for each client. 2. A list of all users' full name, email addresses, titles/positions, and phone numbers that should be set up with a log-in (please note: we do not support group email addresses); 3. Companys full business address
Once we create your company and users on our site, you will be able access Counterparty Manager and enter your entity information and fill out the appropriate representations.
Please note: you will need an LEI number for your entities to use this service. For example a CICI number from: www.gmeiutility.org
To assist you in using the system, I have attached our user guide. In addition, we have a number of pre-recorded webcasts which are available for your information here: http://www.markit.com/product/isda-amend
Once you are ready to fill out your entity information on Counterparty Manager, the below are the mandatory fields that will be needed during the process:
Full Legal Entity Name Entity Type Country of Domicile Principal Business LEI / Entity ID Registered Address
Please feel free to contact me should you have any further questions.
Kind regards,
